data.title: The Groundbreaking Story of RuPaul
data.meta_description: This is everything you need to know about RuPaul's groundbreaking story. Plenty of drag queens have made a career out their craft like Lady Bunny, Dame Edna Everage and Divine. But RuPaul has carved out a place as arguably the biggest name in modern drag, and he's the figurehead who has brought that art to the masses. From his upbringing in California, to studying performing arts in Georgia, to becoming the Queen of New York City and starting 'RuPaul's Drag Race', join MsMojo as we recount The Groundbreaking Story of RuPaul.
data.text:
VOICE OVER: Phoebe de Jeu WRITTEN BY: Owen Maxwell

This is everything you need to know about RuPaul's groundbreaking story. Plenty of drag queens have made a career out their craft like Lady Bunny, Dame Edna Everage and Divine. But RuPaul has carved out a place as arguably the biggest name in modern drag, and he's the figurehead who has brought that art to the masses. From his upbringing in California, to studying performing arts in Georgia, to becoming the Queen of New York City and starting 'RuPaul's Drag Race', join MsMojo as we recount The Groundbreaking Story of RuPaul.
